data.description: Great country home located on quiet cul-de-sac, just minutes from the loop. Enjoy a 30x40 insulated shop with 220v electric, skylights and gas line.  A 12x20 detached building has 3/4 bath, could be used for a number of things.  Wood privacy fence around backyard and additional chain link on back of property. Extra parking.  This cozy home has a wood burning fireplace, large dining area and large utility room.
